These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
2 different pets are kept: hedgehog, frog
There are 2 different favourite colors: blue, green
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, july
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far right##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the person who likes blue is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Pet       | frog       | hedgehog |
| Color         | green | blue  |
| Birthday       | july    | march    |
| Transport   | jet-ski       | bike      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, lemonade
City: prague, nizza
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, alhambra
2 different pets are kept: rat, hedgehog
1. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
2. the person traveling to prague is on the far left##1
3. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Beverage      | lemonade     | almond-milk |
| City           | prague | nizza      |
| Cigar   | alhambra  | tiparillo      |
| Pet         | rat | hedgehog     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: hiking, board-games
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: sunflower, marigold
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, country
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, game
1. the fan of country is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is the game-smoker##1
3. the person who growssunflower is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Hobby      | hiking | board-games  |
| Flower          | sunflower    | marigold   |
| Music-Genre   | country  | ambient   |
| Cigar     | game     | blend |

